column5: Hi all,  getting to grips with the back log of videos I have from last year, here is a video of a late summer trip to Lac seul wit da fam. Net man Jack was on good form. Can't wait for summer again!
I think Roloff needs his own rod!!!! HH
Nice to see the fam out and about!!!  That new boat sure is a nice upgrade Simon!!!  Just noticed I was no longer subscribed to your YouTube channel. Well got that fixed promptly lol
I think Roloff needs his own rod!!!! HH Same, and ice rod on the collar should do just fine
that raft is classic!!!! great day   just need a "Wilson"
Jack's quite the enthusiastic little character. I could watch him fishing all day. Just like when the 2 older grandaughters (5 and 6) are in the boat.
